                            <comment id="14047178" author="busbey" created="Sun, 29 Jun 2014 17:33:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Take a look at &lt;a href=&quot;http://avro.apache.org/docs/1.7.6/api/java/org/apache/avro/reflect/package-summary.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;the Java reflection API&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Getting a schema looks like:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
