&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/11866466/using-apache-avro-reflect&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;the example from Doug on StackOverflow for a working example&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
